334
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:56,000
- No procrastination on drawings. 
 - Unlimited revisions.

335
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:57,100
A soulless clock-in machine.

336
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:59,840
You can't be carefree like the wind!

337
00:26:04,380 --> 00:26:06,380
Did we scare you?

338
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:07,450
All that was just nonsense.

339
00:26:07,450 --> 00:26:09,850
We actually have a very relaxed work atmosphere.

340
00:26:09,850 --> 00:26:12,080
Our mission is to create joy within.

341
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:13,860
Okay, you're off work for today.

342
00:26:13,860 --> 00:26:16,830
When you come to work tomorrow, you'll understand after experiencing it.

343
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:18,510

344
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:20,710

345
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,780
The follow-up purpose and plans

346
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:34,980
will be expanded as soon as possible.

347
00:26:34,980 --> 00:26:40,450
I'm actually more curious about your plans with Anxin for the future.

348
00:26:40,450 --> 00:26:42,890
Is this your brotherly concern?

349
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:48,140
As a brother who once loved her and will always love her in the future.

350
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:50,580
That makes me feel quite threatened.

351
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:53,410
A little sense of danger isn't a bad thing.

352
00:26:54,210 --> 00:26:57,380
Don't worry. Anxin is the person I love.

353
00:26:57,380 --> 00:26:59,300
And she's my family.

354
00:27:08,420 --> 00:27:10,070
What are you doing?

355
00:27:11,680 --> 00:27:15,460
Pretending to be proper and polite is so exhausting. And I don't even know how.

356
00:27:15,460 --> 00:27:19,570
I already have a boss in the family. Can't I just illustrate my comic?

357
00:27:19,570 --> 00:27:21,750
You'll learn over time. Artist Anxin,

358
00:27:21,750 --> 00:27:24,440
our company's ancient-style comic, "I Accidentally Picked Up a Prince,"

359
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:26,440
already has its single volume edition in process.

360
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:29,580
But you have to change the name. The market already has many pirated copies with that name.

361
00:27:29,580 --> 00:27:31,670
Disgusting.

362
00:27:31,670 --> 00:27:35,550
Okay. Boss. Boss's wife.

363
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:38,110
Let this hard worker think about it back home, okay?

364
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:39,880
Good luck.

365
00:27:41,410 --> 00:27:42,800
Look!

366
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:50,960
Young Boss's Wife, is it time to go home?

367
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:53,840
I am considered one of the bosses here.

368
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:57,860
From what you say, you should be the young Boss's wife.

369
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:04,790

370
00:28:04,790 --> 00:28:07,490

371
00:28:12,630 --> 00:28:16,510
We're dating, not playing a video game that requires accomplishing monster-killing tasks to level up.

372
00:28:16,520 --> 00:28:18,330
Work habit.

373
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:23,150
Actually,

374
00:28:23,150 --> 00:28:25,420
