375
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:29,680
but it's just with the intention of making up for lost time.

376
00:28:29,690 --> 00:28:33,040
There are still a lot of things we haven't said

377
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:36,170
and a lot of things we haven't done.

378
00:28:40,870 --> 00:28:44,460
Since that's the case, let's take it slowly.

379
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:47,370
After all, we still have a lot of time.

380
00:29:42,010 --> 00:29:44,250
 My current state,

381
00:29:45,790 --> 00:29:48,060
 you must be very disappointed.

382
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:51,790
 I'm very disappointed,

383
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:57,620
 but all of the worry

384
00:29:58,270 --> 00:30:00,110
 and doubts in my heart

385
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:03,790
 have all fallen to the ground.

386
00:30:03,790 --> 00:30:05,860
 It's so steady.

387
00:30:11,300 --> 00:30:14,110
 I only have myself to blame for all of this.

388
00:30:23,390 --> 00:30:26,470
You can begin a new life for yourself.

389
00:30:26,470 --> 00:30:29,060
I won't continue bothering you or dragging you down.

390
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:36,550
 These days...

391
00:30:37,950 --> 00:30:41,170
 I keep thinking back

392
00:30:41,170 --> 00:30:44,080
to things that happened when we were young.

393
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:45,980
Those...

394
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:50,890
pure and blissful times,

395
00:30:50,890 --> 00:30:53,410
when all we had to worry about was the homework we couldn't finish

396
00:30:56,430 --> 00:31:00,310
 and the exams we had.

397
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,800
 I would also think about how

398
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:09,800
hypothetically, if everything could be relived,

399
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:15,100
 If the person I had met first had been you,

400
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:20,200
 would everything have been different?

401
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:37,500
 I'm sorry.

402
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:49,000
 I can finally understand you

403
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:53,000
 and how you felt at the time.

404
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:54,800
 You wouldn't understand.

405
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:57,800
 How could I not understand?

406
00:31:57,800 --> 00:32:00,700
 Haven't I always been waiting for someone?

407
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,800
Waking up in the early morning every day,

408
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:09,400
there are things to be done,

409
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,400
places to go,

410
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:17,200
 and a person who needs me, waiting for me.

411
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:21,800
 How is it that you can always show up on time whenever I'm feeling down?

412
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:24,500
 I want to know if he's living well,

413
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:27,200
I want to resolve his worries for him.

414
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:30,000
 I want him to be able to have no more concerns

415
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:32,600
 and to have no more need to fear.

416
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:38,000
 I also hope that every day,

417
00:32:38,000 --> 00:32:39,800
 he can be very carefree

418
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:44,500
 and happy. I hope that he can smile as much as he wishes.

419
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:49,010
 Did you know?

420
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:53,000
 To me, these things

421
00:32:53,780 --> 00:32:56,380
 bring me the most happiness now.

422
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:11,840
I'm not worthy of giving you happiness.

423
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:15,250
I also don't hope

424
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:18,100
 that after you see my ugly past,

425
00:33:18,100 --> 00:33:21,400
 you still choose to stand by my side.

426
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,800
 Anyway,

427
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:36,600
 in the times we were together,

428
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:40,600
 I was already so happy.

429
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:42,100
Ling Sheng!

430
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:03,000
 Look.

431
00:34:06,790 --> 00:34:09,850
I've already made my preparations.

432
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:14,400
I will repay all of those days you waited for me alone

433
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:19,200
 with the rest of my life.

434
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:25,000
 I also hope there will be a day where you will turn back and look at me.

435
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:30,000
 As long as you nod once,

436
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:35,400
 I can also accelerate my pace and run to you like mad.

437
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:39,600
 To me, Xin'er is just like the moon in the sky.

438
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:42,600
 Wonderful, luminous.

439
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:44,600
 In order to get closer to her,

440
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:47,800
 I prepared for many, many years.

441
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:52,100
 Now, I am finally standing by her side

442
00:34:52,100 --> 00:34:54,400
