443
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:56,400
 Smiling with her,

444
00:34:56,400 --> 00:35:00,500
 crying together, and growing old together.

445
00:35:00,500 --> 00:35:02,800
 Whenever, I think about this,

446
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:06,600
 I feel like I'm happier than any person in the world.

447
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:11,400
 And I will definitely bring her happiness.

448
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:17,300
So don't make me wait too long.

449
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:16,600
Did you sign the Super Topic today?

