454
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:30,600
if we are being rubbed off of, we must not be soft on them, and the people who change their fandom but not their username...

455
00:36:30,600 --> 00:36:34,700
You are an extraordinary talent and a fandom miracle!

456
00:36:41,200 --> 00:36:44,000
Enough, Anxin, stop taking pictures! You're already pretty enough.

457
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:47,200
I wasn't taking pictures! I was checking whether there were any vegetables in my teeth and things like that.

458
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:50,800
I'm a public figure, after all. Check out my smile!

459
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:52,600
Good, my big star.

460
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:55,600
Your mission for today is to finish signing all of them.

